\c 3
\s Vana vaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino ava vanakomana vaDhavhidhi vakamuberekerwa paHebhuroni: Dangwe Amunoni, kuna Ahinowamu muJezireeri; wepiri Dhaniyeri, kuna Abhigairi muKarimeri;
\v 2 wetatu Abhusaromu mwanakomana waMaaka mukunda waTarimai mambo weGeshuri; wechina Adhoniya mwanakomana waHagiti;
\v 3 weshanu Shefatia, kuna Abhitari; wetanhatu Itireami, kuna Egira mukadzi wake\x + 2 Sam. 3.2-5.\x*.
\v 4 Vatanhatu vakaberekerwa kwaari paHebhuroni; ndokutongapo makore manomwe nemwedzi mitanhatu\x + 2 Sam. 2.11.\x*; uye paJerusarema wakatonga makore makumi matatu nematatu\x + 29.27. 2 Sam. 5.5.\x*\x + 2 Sam. 2.11.\x*.
\v 5 Ava vakaberekerwa iye paJerusarema: Shimea, naShobhabhu, naNatani\x + 14.4-7. 2 Sam. 5.14-16.\x*, naSoromoni\x + 2 Sam. 12.24.\x*, \add vari\add* vana, kuna Bhatishuwa mukunda waAmieri;
\v 6 naIbhari, naErishama, naErifereti,
\v 7 naNoga, naNefegi, naJafia,
\v 8 naErishama, naEriadha, naErifereti, \add vari\add* vapfumbamwe.
\v 9 Vese vaiva vanakomana vaDhavhidhi, kusingaverengwi vanakomana vevarongo; uye Tamari hanzvadzi yavo\x + 2 Sam. 13.1.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Nemwanakomana waSoromoni waiva Rehobhoamu\x + 1 Madz. 11.43.\x*; Abhia mwanakomana wake; Asa mwanakomana wake\x + 1 Madz. 15.8.\x*; Jehoshafati mwanakomana wake\x + 1 Madz. 15.24.\x*;
\v 11 Joramu mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 8.16,24.\x*; Ahaziya mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 8.16,24.\x*; Joashi mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 11.2.\x*;
\v 12 Amaziya mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 12.21.\x*; Azariya mwanakomana wake; Jotamu mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 15.7.\x*;
\v 13 Ahazi mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 15.38.\x*; Hezekia mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 16.20.\x*; Manase mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 20.21.\x*;
\v 14 Amoni mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 21.18.\x*; Josiya mwanakomana wake\x + 2 Madz. 21.26.\x*.
\v 15 Nevanakomana vaJosiya: Dangwe Johwanani, wepiri Jehoyakimu, wetatu Zedhekia, wechina Sharumi.
\v 16 Nevanakomana vaJehoyakimu: Jekoniya mwanakomana wake, Zedhekia mwanakomana wake\x + Mat. 1.11.\x*.
\v 17 Nevanakomana vaJekoniya: Asiri, Shearitieri mwanakomana wake,
\v 18 naMarikirami, naPedhaya, naShenazari, Jekamia, Hoshama, naNedhabhia.
\v 19 Nevanakomana vaPedhaya: Zerubhabheri, naShimei. Nevanakomana vaZerubhabheri: Meshurami, naHananiya, naSheromiti hanzvadzi yavo,
\v 20 naHashubha, naOheri, naBherekia, naHasadhia, Jushabhiheshedhi, \add vari\add* vashanu.
\v 21 Zvino vanakomana vaHananiya: Peratia, naJeshaya. Vanakomana vaRefaya, vanakomana vaArinani, vanakomana vaObhadhiya, vanakomana vaShekaniya.
\v 22 Nevanakomana vaShekaniya: Shemaya. Nevanakomana vaShemaya: Hatushi, naIgari, naBharia, naNearia, naShafati, \add vari\add* vatanhatu.
\v 23 Nevanakomana vaNearia: Erioenai, naHizikia, naAzirikamu, \add vari\add* vatatu.
\v 24 Nevanakomana vaErioenai: Hodhavhia, naEriashibhi, naPeraya, naAkubhi, naJohwanani, naDheraya, naAnani, \add vari\add* vanomwe.